"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, this is Scotty over in Neadville, Texas, doing our regenerative agriculture project. This is a layer of green beans put directly on the ground. In the past, we had put a layer of carbon down first, like some leaves or some wood chips. Then I read in this great book, Pay Dirt, that maybe you should put the green, uh the high nitrogen stuff down first so that you can get a good layer of bacteria going on the actual ground and kind of inoculate the ground so that future piles will go a little bit quicker. So that's what we did this time. Next layer up is a carbon layer. Anyway, thanks y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, this is Scotty over in Neadville, Texas, doing our regenerative agriculture project.\",\n      \"start\": 0.56,\n      \"end\": 5.6,\n      \"duration\": 5.04,\n      \"confidence\": 0.993,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.998\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\": 0.88,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 0.96,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.04,\n          \"end\": 1.2,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.2,\n          \"end\": 1.28,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \",\",\n          \"start\": 1.28,\n          \"end\": 1.36,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.971\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" this\",\n          \"start\": 1.36,\n          \"